<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Detail Program Pendidikan - Relawan Nusantara</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-dark: #0a0f1e;
            --accent-cyan: #00d2ff;
            --card-bg: #1e293b;
            --text-gray: #94a3b8;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--bg-dark);
            color: white;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Navbar Sederhana */
        .navbar {
            padding: 20px 5%;
            background: rgba(10, 15, 30, 0.9);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
        }

        .back-link {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--accent-cyan);
            font-weight: 600;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        /* Container Utama */
        .container {
            max-width: 850px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .hero-img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 380px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        }

        .content-card {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            margin-top: -60px;
            position: relative;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
        }

        h1 { color: var(--accent-cyan); margin: 0 0 15px 0; font-size: 2.2rem; }
        .description { color: #cbd5e1; margin-bottom: 30px; font-size: 0.95rem; }

        /* Grid Informasi */
        .info-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 35px;
        }

        .info-item {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 210, 255, 0.1);
        }

        .info-item h4 {
            margin: 0 0 8px 0;
            color: var(--accent-cyan);
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .info-item p { margin: 0; font-weight: 600; font-size: 1rem; }

        /* Tombol */
        .btn-register {
            display: block;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #00f2fe, #0077ff);
            color: #0a0f1e;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 800;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
        }

        .btn-register:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 242, 254, 0.4);
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) { .info-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav class="navbar">
        <a href="/pendidikan" class="back-link">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" fill="currentColor"><path d="M15.41 16.59L10.83 12l4.58-4.59L14 6l-6 6 6 6z"></path></svg>
            Kembali ke Program
        </a>
        <div style="font-weight: bold; color: var(--accent-cyan);">Relawan Nusantara</div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1524178232363-1fb2b075b655?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop" class="hero-img" alt="Kelas Inspirasi">
        
        <div class="content-card">
            <h1>Kelas Inspirasi Anak Negeri</h1>
            <p class="description">
                Jadilah bagian dari perubahan! Program ini mengajak kamu untuk berbagi ilmu, cerita profesi, dan memotivasi anak-anak di pelosok negeri agar mereka berani bermimpi setinggi langit.
            </p>
            
            <div class="info-grid">
                <div class="info-item">
                    <h4>üìÖ Jadwal Mengajar</h4>
                    <p>Sabtu, 10:00 - 12:00 WIB</p>
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <h4>üë• Kuota Relawan</h4>
                    <p>Tersisa 25 Slot</p>
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <h4>üìù Tugas Utama</h4>
                    <p>Mengajar & Bermain Edukatif</p>
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <h4>üèÖ Reward Koin</h4>
                    <p>30 Koin Aktivitas</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <button id="btnDaftar" class="btn-register">Daftar Sekarang</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        document.getElementById('btnDaftar').addEventListener('click', () => {
            // Update Koin di LocalStorage
            let currentCoins = parseInt(localStorage.getItem('relawan_koin')) || 0;
            currentCoins += 30;
            localStorage.setItem('relawan_koin', currentCoins);
            
            alert("Pendaftaran Berhasil! üéâ\nKamu mendapatkan +30 Koin. Sampai jumpa di kelas!");
            window.location.href = "/pendidikan"; // Balik ke halaman utama
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>